./runs/20260529-163436-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7151:      "note": "The human problem the synthesis targets: practitioners who import the wrong relationship to effort across traditions, producing burnout, shame, passivity, or spiritual pride."
